module MetaC-ID
language MetaC

start symbol Constant

test CONS 1 [[1]] parse succeeds
test CONS 12 [[12]] parse succeeds
test CONS a [[a]] parse fails

test CONS_BINARY [[bin<001010>]] parse succeeds
test CONS_NON_BINARY [[bin<002010>]] parse fails
test CONS_HEX [[hex<cacca>]] parse succeeds
test CONS_NON_HEX [[hex<vacca>]] parse fails
test CONS_OCTAL [[oct<71>]] parse succeeds
test CONS_NON_OCTAL [[0xA]] parse fails

